To change the linux fonts:
    1.search and download font file(*.ttf)
    2.go to the dir-->/usr/share/fonts
    3.mkdir $(name of the fonts)
    4.cp the font file into the new make direction
    5.update the fonts cache
    ...mkfontscale
    ...mkfontdir
    ...fc-cache

P.S.
    Be sure that you get the root access
